      "range": "20772-20819",
      "markText": "张无忌突然间记起了《九阳真经》中的几句话：“他强由他强，清风拂山冈。他横任他横，明月照大江。”",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=20772&rangeEnd=20819",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=20772&rangeEnd=20819"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_61_15267-15299",
      "chapterUid": 61,
      "range": "15267-15299",
      "markText": "芷若成了寡妇，能不能再跟我重续前缘？”想到此处，不由得怦然心动。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=61&rangeStart=15267&rangeEnd=15299",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=61&rangeStart=15267&rangeEnd=15299"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_55_10459-10506",
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "range": "10459-10506",
      "markText": "“他写了‘门户有变，亟须清理’八个字，咱们武当门下，难道还会出什么败类不成？莫非无忌这孩子……",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=10459&rangeEnd=10506",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=10459&rangeEnd=10506"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_10_12902-12947",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "12902-12947",
      "markText": "但在这荒野山地，哪里有甚吃的，张君宝去了半日，只采得一大把草莓来。三人胡乱吃了，倚石休息。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=12902&rangeEnd=12947",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=12902&rangeEnd=12947"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_18_17615-17667",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "17615-17667",
      "markText": "“张真人既不肯赐教，那么我们师兄弟三人，逐一向武当六侠中的三人请教，三阵分胜败，三阵中胜得两阵者为赢。”",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=17615&rangeEnd=17667",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=17615&rangeEnd=17667"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_27_26497-26538",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "26497-26538",
      "markText": "詹春便道：“好罢，我会送她去。”心中却想：“昆仑山横亘千里，我怎知坐忘峰在哪里？”",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=26497&rangeEnd=26538",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=26497&rangeEnd=26538"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_43_20791-20845",
      "chapterUid": 43,
      "range": "20791-20845",
      "markText": "后来朱元璋、徐达、邓愈、汤和等行军打仗，果然恪遵张无忌的令旨，不敢随便杀戮无辜，终于民心归顺，得成一代大业。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=43&rangeStart=20791&rangeEnd=20845",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=43&rangeStart=20791&rangeEnd=20845"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_14_8734-8781",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "8734-8781",
      "markText": "殷素素接了过来披在肩头，感到袍上还带着张翠山身上的温暖，心头甜丝丝的，忍不住在黑暗中嫣然微笑。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=8734&rangeEnd=8781",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=8734&rangeEnd=8781"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_64_2425-2509",
      "chapterUid": 64,
      "range": "2425-2509",
      "markText": "周芷若对张无忌说：“你只管和她做夫妻、生娃娃，过得十年八年，你心里就只会想着我，不舍得我了。”这种感情，小弟弟、小妹妹们是不懂的。所以我不主张十三四岁的小妹妹们写小说。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=64&rangeStart=2425&rangeEnd=2509",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=64&rangeStart=2425&rangeEnd=2509"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_11_21141-21213",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "21141-21213",
      "markText": "都大锦主理龙门镖局二十余年，江湖上的奇事也不知见过多少，但以二千两黄金的镖金来托保一个活人，别说自己手里从未接过，只怕天下各处的镖行也闻所未闻。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=21141&rangeEnd=21213",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=21141&rangeEnd=21213"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_11_35653-35691",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "35653-35691",
      "markText": "张三丰道：“不是几百年，最多不过七八十年，当我年轻之时，就没听过这几句话。”",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=35653&rangeEnd=35691",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=35653&rangeEnd=35691"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_16_12647-12743",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "12647-12743",
      "markText": "谢逊道：“你心地仁厚，原该福泽无尽，但于是非善恶之际太过执着，难免厄难重重，你一切小心。无忌胸襟宽广，看来日后行事处世，比你圆通随和得多。五妹虽是女子，却不会吃人的亏。我所耽心的，反倒是你。”",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=12647&rangeEnd=12743",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=12647&rangeEnd=12743"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_63_18881-18904",
      "chapterUid": 63,
      "range": "18881-18904",
      "markText": "真正的人、真正的事，往往不及心中所想的那么好。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=63&rangeStart=18881&rangeEnd=18904",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=63&rangeStart=18881&rangeEnd=18904"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_10_12132-12202",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "12132-12202",
      "markText": "那心禅堂的老僧厉声高喝：“罗汉堂众弟子，何以不并力上前？”罗汉堂一百零八名弟子暴雷也似的应了声：“是！”又在达摩堂十八弟子之外围了三个圈子。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=12132&rangeEnd=12202",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=12132&rangeEnd=12202"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_11_411-445",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "411-445",
      "markText": "花开花落，花落花开。少年子弟江湖老，红颜少女的鬓边终于也见到了白发。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=411&rangeEnd=445",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=411&rangeEnd=445"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_13_4315-4366",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "4315-4366",
      "markText": "那少女道：“不单都大锦走了眼，连我也上了大当。我早该想到武当七侠英姿飒爽，怎会是如此险鸷粗鲁的人物。”",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4315&rangeEnd=4366",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4315&rangeEnd=4366"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_13_7311-7335",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "7311-7335",
      "markText": "那少女恨恨的道：“送了性命最好，反正是你害的。”",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=7311&rangeEnd=7335",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=7311&rangeEnd=7335"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_13_8290-8382",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "8290-8382",
      "markText": "那少女沉着脸道：“你上岸去罢，我再也不要见你啦！”张翠山给她这一掌打得羞怒交迸，说道：“好！我倒没见过这般任性无礼的姑娘！”跨步走上船头。那少女冷笑道：“你没见过，今日便要给你见见。”",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8290&rangeEnd=8382",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8290&rangeEnd=8382"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300180297_14_9000-9059",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "9000-9059",
      "markText": "轻轻移身到殷素素身旁，想在她耳畔悄声说句话，哪知殷素素适于此时转过脸来。二人两下里一凑，张翠山的嘴唇正好碰上了她右颊。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300180297&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=9000&rangeEnd=9059",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/87c32550813abacedg017648?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=9000&rangeEnd=9059"
